text: Tel Aviv on Fire (Hebrew: תל אביב על האש, Tel Aviv Al Ha'Esh) is a 2018 Luxembourgian Israeli French Belgian comedy drama movie directed by Sameh Zoabi and starring Kais Nashef, Yaniv Bitton, Maisa Abd Alhady, Lubna Azabal. ==Other websites== * * Category:2018 comedy-drama movies Category:Luxembourgian comedy movies Category:Luxembourgian drama movies Category:Israeli movies Category:French comedy movies Category:French drama movies Category:Belgian comedy movies Category:Belgian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Sameh Zoabi
title: Tel Aviv on Fire
